say | wolf | This is one of Tallinn University dormitories, called Karu 17.
say | wolf | Once you have visited a new place, it will be added to the Notebook in the right corner of your screen.
say | wolf | University provides three obtions for international students. I recommend looking at Karu 17 first, as it is the closet just a 10 minute walk, and located in city center.
say | wolf | You can explore the town and finding necessary items very comfortably during the beginning of the semester.
say | wolf | It is importance to book accommodation beforehand. Go check out www.tlu.ee/en/accommodation for details on all three options.
say | wolf | After settling down in your new home, let's get ready for school! 
say | wolf | The most important event is Orientation day. You will recieve crucial details about your documents and how to proceed correctly.
say | wolf | Let's practice going to university from here so you won't be late on such a big day!
